For the past few weeks, the line up for fuel in City Flora petrol station is usually 3~4 times longer compare to other petrol station at same location. The situation is getting worse day after day. Meanwhile, City Flora didn’t even bother to add the fuel to make line up shorter. Thus, I would say they are the most undesired petrol station in Yangon.

On 26 November 2018, two days after fuel crisis, as usual, I want to fill up fuel at the same petrol station to go my workplace as usual and the line up is too long.
